snippet.title: Cargo demo (Blender snail adventure game)
snippet.description:
Cargo is a 3D adventure game about a snail who has been robbed! Download the game: http://phatcore.com/alex/?p=177

The player controls Cargo, exploring the environment from a snail's point of view. You can climb walls, crawl on the ceiling, and roll and float in your shell.

Music by Robert Leigh.

Please excuse the poor quality of my recording equipment.
